{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"With users spread all around the globe, it’s more important than ever to pay attention to how they expect to see information in your apps. Formatting currency and dates in the user’s preferred way can make the difference between a frustrating experience and a great app. Handling different locales properly doesn’t take a lot of work and can broaden the reach of your application. Come see how you can add an international flair to your app today."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc12-244-internationalization-tips-and-tricks"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12-244-Internationalization-Tips-and-Tricks","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC12","title":"Internationalization Tips and Tricks","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/244\/","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","type":"reference"}},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC12":{"abstract":[{"text":"iOS 6, macOS 10.8 (Mountain Lion).","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/ww